Install SeeboMini

	1 Insert the SD card in SeeboMini device(M8-S802)
	2 Using a sharp non-conductive object to press the recovery button
	3 In SeeboMini device, this is located in the AV connector
	4 Keep pressing, and connect the power, until you see a RED SCREEN
	5 Release button and waiting for an animated Android with a progress bar showing
	6 The device will then automatically reboot, and start with the our Seebo TV firmware updating
	7 Don't remove your SD card until loading Seebo TV
